FBIS3-12584 "drnes042_l_94001" FBIS-NES-94-042 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Mar 1994 ISRAEL Rabin Reportedly To Cut U.S. Visit `in Half' TA0203185694 Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network in Hebrew 1800 GMT 2 Mar 94 TA0203185694 Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network in Hebrew 1800 GMT 2 Mar 94 Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] Before we close this newscast, we have another update: The prime minister has decided to cut short his visit to the United States, planned to begin in 10 days, due to the situation in the territories. Our political correspondent Gadi Sukenik has learned that at this stage, the visit is planned to be cut in half and will apparently include only meetings with the heads of the state and a few meetings with leaders of the U.S. Jewry.
